[I] Audio player

[T] DeaDBeeF (as in 0xDEADBEEF) is a modular cross-platform audio player.
[T] DeaDBeeF plays a variety of audio formats, converts between them, lets you
[T] customize the UI in almost any way you want, and use many additional
[T] plugins which can extend it even more.

[U] https://deadbeef.sourceforge.io/

[A] Oleksiy Yakovenko
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/audio
[F] CROSS NO-LTO

[L] GPL
[V] 1.10.3

[D] 9a45bc8493046c23b6c82ca5732a45a885be0a444d812181cd5e7d5a deadbeef-1.10.3.tar.bz2 https://download.sourceforge.net/deadbeef/

var_append GCC_WRAPPER_APPEND ' ' -L$root$(pkgprefix libdir libx11)
CC=${CC/gcc/clang} CXX=${CXX/g++/clang++}

var_append confopt ' ' "--enable-gtk3 --disable-gtk2"
